 of the Poisson-Gamma model: if we consider ratios of neighboring\nPoisson-Gamma probabilities, then these are linearly related to the counts of\nrepeated identifications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2011 09:43:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-28"}
